{"tid":2384315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史上的今天！小智遺棄大比鳥22週年 網友加碼曝「四大悲劇」","createTime":"2021-01-28T13:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T14:07:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"174f053329659da6e2a0bbe37a9e9741aa46e8c8","tid":2384315,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/01/28/phppoUxq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F01%2F28%2FphppoUxq8.jpg&h=43db86e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」表示，今日是小智遺棄「比雕」的22週年。（圖取自臉書專頁「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taiwanmemess/posts/712038512792932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaiwanmemess%2Fposts%2F712038512792932&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUt7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=3e9d8902\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/taiwanmemess/posts/712038512792932</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/28 19:36<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕在台灣曾經翻譯為「神奇寶貝」的日本動漫「精靈寶可夢」（pokemon）是不少人童年的回憶。而臉書專頁「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」就發文表示，今（28）日是神奇寶貝故事主角小智遺棄「比雕」的22週年，貼文一出讓不少人笑翻，更有網友留言「四大悲劇」，令人莞爾。<br />\n<br />\n「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」貼出一張神奇寶貝主角小智與比雕的對話，只見小智對比雕說，「我看你就留在這個森林哩，等事情辦完以後我會馬上回來」，但沒想到比雕這一等就再也沒有看到小智，首播距今已22年。<br />\n<br />\n「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」也搞笑的替小智設計對白，「記者：小智你為什麼要遺棄比雕？渣智：我沒把它放進寶貝球裡面，這不算收服，所以我沒有遺棄他喔。」<br />\n<br />\n「台灣迷因 taiwan meme」更貼立委林昶佐的照片假裝替比雕發聲，「比雕後來因為自己被遺棄，對法律感到失望，於是後來他勵志（立志）的選上了立委，在立法院內為動物權益改革持續努力著。」<br />\n<br />\n網友看到貼文後也紛紛留言，「等等這個事情辦完也太久了吧，瞬間遺忘22年」、「你是忘記了還是害怕想起來」、「就算回去比雕認不認的出現在畫風的小智也是個問題XDDD」；也有網友寫下「四大悲劇」，「主人不來領的比雕、永遠到不了大都的張敏、無法上岸的酷拉皮卡、選了五屆還是無法當總統的宋楚瑜（其中4次角逐總統、1次競選副總統）」。"},{"pid":"97ce8af3871a422bc63463097faec4e4f7ebea2e","tid":2384315,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"棄養係台灣算唔算犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ef468db20cc5debac61eca58b4d0da6755a8b1","tid":2384315,"uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:33:52.000Z","msg":"咁事情真係未辦完<br />\n而家仲係10歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5931f909b7c8e993d6b8ae3a81af9c5646e4ff","tid":2384315,"uid":28367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"伏筆呢家野佢識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259be81c96e2a99c67074d15592304f48a9eed02","tid":2384315,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"未搵到mega石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921d543ca91865ab94b976122f9d02873575a085","tid":2384315,"uid":34685,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"無法上岸的酷拉皮卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佳爺自首先定hxh大結局先？"},{"pid":"791682c74a15bb2b234fe95a825dbd4277c14b5b","tid":2384315,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef5931f909b7c8e993d6b8ae3a81af9c5646e4ff","tid":2384315,"uid":28367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"伏筆呢家野佢識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"諗起one piece條鯨魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班死忠話尾田留左伏筆好神"},{"pid":"0da7b599b83da504a200a2636b83c9f9cc40f67f","tid":2384315,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"一日未贏到聯盟冠軍 一日都唔會返黎接佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}